string = str(input("Enter any word:"))

i = 0

for x in string :
   
 print("The character at",i,"index is:",x)
  
  i=i+1


Output :-

Enter any word:madhu

The character at 0 index is: m

The character at 1 index is: a

The character at 2 index is: d

The character at 3 index is: h

The character at 4 index is: u